snippet.textDisplay:
Man it's wild seeing the types of spin-off games that have come from Dungeon Fighter Online as one of the original US players of that MMO beat-em-up/RPG from almost 15 years ago. Everyone knows about the fighting game (DNF Duel) by now, though at least.

Especially since this game focuses on one of the Slayer subclasses (berserker is actually my LEAST favorite Slayer sub-class, but I guess it works for a Soulslike game).

snippet.textDisplay:
@fightingcowboy, dont mean to tell you how to play but trust me on this, pick a weapon you wanna stick with before you start demo, been playing this game and testing it so much i could do a walkthrough lol,

"ALWAYS" upgrade Will power to 15 then do endurance dont need vitality yet (if your going for heavy sword that not gonna cut) but since your playing dual sword based of your last game play you wanna go in order:
Willpower 15
Endurance 15
Strength 15
Then maybe health if your struggling to 12
Rest pump will power to 30
Then endurance 22
Strenth 20
Then rest will power
Dont exceed endurance above 22 nor vitality above 22 the returns aint worth it,

My build is spear, OMG spear is OP stats to really see spear do well:
Vitality 12
Endurance 15
Strength 10
Willpower 15
Proficiency 20
